do to her?

1268
01:28:39,154 --> 01:28:41,690
<i>...kill us if he got the chance.</i>

1269
01:28:44,655 --> 01:28:47,570
<i>I think he's been
recording my telephone.</i>

1270
01:28:49,657 --> 01:28:52,572
<i>Listen, I'd better get back.
It's almost 2:00.</i>

1271
01:28:52,700 --> 01:28:54,572
<i>No, please don't
go back there.</i>

1272
01:28:54,700 --> 01:28:56,489
<i>Not just yet.</i>

1273
01:28:56,616 --> 01:29:00,861
<i>All right.
All right, honey. I won't.</i>

1274
01:29:04,994 --> 01:29:06,368
15,000 bucks.

1275
01:29:06,494 --> 01:29:10,739
That's not bad for a day's work,
is it, Mr. Caul?

1276
01:29:10,871 --> 01:29:12,945
What'll he do
with them?

1277
01:29:15,372 --> 01:29:16,402
We'll see.

1278
01:29:25,583 --> 01:29:29,411
<i>...kill us if he got the chance.</i>

1279
01:29:39,586 --> 01:29:43,712
<i>Later in the week.
Sunday, maybe.</i>

1280
01:29:46,463 --> 01:29:48,335
<i>Sunday, definitely.</i>

1281
01:29:51,631 --> 01:29:53,289
<i>The Jack Tar Hotel.</i>

1282
01:29:54,840 --> 01:29:56,831
<i>3:00.</i>

1283
01:29:56,965 --> 01:29:58,956
<i>Room 773.</i>

1284
01:30:01,050 --> 01:30:02,211
Uh...

1285
01:30:02,342 --> 01:30:06,123
I wonder if you could give me
room 773.

1286
01:30:06,260 --> 01:30:08,297
773?

1287
01:30:09,677 --> 01:30:11,633
That is occupied, sir.

1288
01:30:15,012 --> 01:30:17,880
The rooms are all
basically the same, however.

1289
01:30:18,013 --> 01:30:18,961
Well...

1290
01:30:22,222 --> 01:30:25,091
Do you have a room
that would be, uh...

1291
01:30:25,223 --> 01:30:26,597
adjoining, uh...
close by?

1292
01:30:26,723 --> 01:30:28,382
Adjoining, just...

1293
01:30:28,516 --> 01:30:30,257
Yes, I do.

1294
01:30:30,391 --> 01:30:31,304
You do.

1295
01:34:42,205 --> 01:34:45,039
I'm tired of this lying,
all right?

1296
01:34:55,083 --> 01:34:57,121
<i>I can't stand it.</i>

1297
01:34:57,250 --> 01:34:59,538
<i>I can't stand it
any more.</i>

1298
01:34:59,668 --> 01:35:02,038
<i>You're going to make me cry.</i>

1299
01:35:02,169 --> 01:35:04,918
<i>I know. Me, too.</i>

1300
01:35:05,044 --> 01:35:06,288
<i>No, don't.</i>

1301
01:35:06,419 --> 01:35:08,411
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

1302
01:35:08,546 --> 01:35:10,121
No idea!

1303
01:35:10,254 --> 01:35:12,126
This is horrible...

1304
01:35:15,463 --> 01:35:16,838
<i>I love you.</i>

1305
01:36:08,561 --> 01:36:12,009
Aah!

1306
01:36:13,895 --> 01:36:16,728
<i>Aah!</i>

1307
01:36:23,440 --> 01:36:25,763
<i>It was stated that Nixon
would not deliver...</i>

1308
01:36:25,899 --> 01:36:28,684
<i>the State of the Union
message in person...</i>

1309
01:36:39,610 --> 01:36:41,850
<i>Will you cut that out?</i>

1310
01:36:41,985 --> 01:36:44,854
<i>How can you yell
at me like that?</i>

1311
01:36:44,986 --> 01:36:46,361
<i>And in my condition.</i>

1312
01:36:46,487 --> 01:36:49,854
<i>You're not fit to be
the father of my child.</i>

1313
01:36:49,988 --> 01:36:51,362
<i>Oh, what is this?</i>

1314
01:36:51,488 --> 01:36:53,360
<i>I'm trying
to act like Wilma.</i>

1315
01:36:53,488 --> 01:36:55,147
<i>Well, you're
overdoing it.</i>

1316
01:36:59,490 --> 01:37:01,232
<i>All right.
Pull over.</i>

1317
01:37:03,449 --> 01:37:04,943
<i>What's the big rush?</i>

1318
01:37:05,075 --> 01:37:07,280
<i>I'm taking my wife
to the hospital.</i>

1319
01:37:07,409 --> 01:37:08,783
<i>She's having
a baby.</i>

1320
01:37:08,909 --> 01:37:10,616
<i>I got to
hand it to you.</i>

1321
01:37:10,743 --> 01:37:12,022
<i>You got intestinal
fortitude.</i>

1322
01:37:12,160 --> 01:37:13,155
<i>Sit down, Fred.</i>

1323
01:37:13,286 --> 01:37:17,032
<i>You're wearing a groove
in the floor.</i>

1324
01:37:17,162 --> 01:37:18,536
<i>Look at Wilma
out there.</i>

1325
01:37:18,662 --> 01:37:20,534
<i>How can she be so calm...</i>

1326
01:37:20,662 --> 01:37:23,530
<i>when she knows
what I'm going through?</i>

1327
01:37:23,663 --> 01:37:25,037
<i>How are you, Fred?</i>

1328
01:37:25,164 --> 01:37:27,534
<i>How do you
think I am?</i>

1329
01:37:27,664 --> 01:37:29,536
<i>Betty, you go out there...</i>

1330
01:37:29,664 --> 01:37:31,905
<i>and tell Wilma
if she doesn't...</i>

1331
01:41:51,190 --> 01:41:52,268
Wait. Richard!

1332
01:41:52,356 --> 01:41:54,147
I want to see
the director.

1333
01:41:54,274 --> 01:41:55,850
He's not in today.

1334
01:41:57,067 --> 01:41:59,472
I'm afraid you'll
have to leave now.

1335
01:43:58,014 --> 01:43:59,388
Let's clear an aisle.

1336
01:43:59,515 --> 01:44:00,888
Let these people
through.

1337
01:44:01,014 --> 01:44:02,389
Come on,
clear the way.

1338
01:44:02,515 --> 01:44:03,889
We'll answer your
questions upstairs.

1339
01:44:04,015 --> 01:44:05,390
Let these
people through.

1340
01:44:05,516 --> 01:44:07,009
Let these
people through.

1341
01:44:07,141 --> 01:44:08,421
Just one question.

1342
01:44:08,559 --> 01:44:09,553
No, please.

1343
01:44:09,683 --> 01:44:12,302
Do you suspect foul play
in the accident?

1344
01:44:12,434 --> 01:44:14,260
What about your
corporate control?

1345
01:44:14,393 --> 01:44:16,265
Will your stock
now give you...

1346
01:44:16,393 --> 01:44:17,259
controlling interest?

1347
01:44:17,394 --> 01:44:20,013
What kind of insurance
do you have?

1348
01:44:20,145 --> 01:44:21,341
That's
an unfair question.

1349
01:44:26,146 --> 01:44:28,018
<i>What do you think?</i>

1350
01:44:28,146 --> 01:44:31,015
<i>I don't know what
I'm getting him for Christmas.</i>

1351
01:44:31,147 --> 01:44:33,517
<i>He's already
got everything.</i>

1352
01:44:33,648 --> 01:44:36,599
<i>Doesn't need anything any more.</i>

1353
01:44:39,482 --> 01:44:42,517
Do you feel there's an enemy
within the company?

1354
01:44:45,359 --> 01:44:47,232
<i>He's not hurting anybody.</i>

1355
01:44:47,360 --> 01:44:50,027
<i>Neither are we.</i>

1356
01:44:50,152 --> 01:44:52,476
<i>Oh, God.</i>

1357
01:44:52,611 --> 01:44:53,476
...drunk driving?

1358
01:44:58,238 --> 01:44:59,516
<i>I can't stand it.</i>

1359
01:44:59,654 --> 01:45:02,688
<i>I can't stand it
any more.</i>

1360
01:45:02,822 --> 01:45:03,900
Aah!

1361
01:45:06,031 --> 01:45:06,979
Take it!

1362
01:45:07,115 --> 01:45:08,773
<i>Take it!</i>

1363
01:45:13,908 --> 01:45:16,232
<i>Do you think we can do this?</i>

1364
01:45:16,367 --> 01:45:18,275
<i>Later in the week.</i>

1365
01:45:18,409 --> 01:45:21,242
<i>Sunday, maybe.</i>

1366
01:45:21,368 --> 01:45:24,237
<i>Sunday, definitely.</i>

1367
01:45:24,369 --> 01:45:26,160
<i>The Jack Tar Hotel.</i>

1368
01:45:27,495 --> 01:45:28,360
<i>3:00.</i>

1369
01:45:28,495 --> 01:45:30,533
<i>Room 773.</i>

1370
01:45:33,955 --> 01:45:36,870
<i>He'd kill us
if he got the chance.</i>

