01:46:10,131 --> 01:46:11,374
Hello.

1372
01:46:13,132 --> 01:46:14,375
Hello.

1373
01:47:08,145 --> 01:47:09,473
Hello.

1374
01:47:17,022 --> 01:47:18,137
Hello.

1375
01:47:18,273 --> 01:47:20,976
We know that you know, Mr. Caul.

1376
01:47:21,107 --> 01:47:23,976
For your own sake,
don't get involved any further.

1377
01:47:24,108 --> 01:47:25,980
We'll be listening
